            "title": "欧洲股市早段下跌\r\n",
            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">      欧洲股市早段下跌。英国富时100指数报8,727.87点，跌28.34点(0.32%)；德国DAX指数报22,390.18点，跌160.71点(0.71%)；法国CAC 40指数报8,041.48点，跌61.04点(0.75%)。  (WL)</span>\n</div>",
